codex
The D3D11 and D3D9 hemispheric getters themselves match for the sun slot; the suspicious part is not a tangent/back swap. I’m checking the scale-mode setup next because D3D9 conditionally selects scaled vs unscaled light accessors, while D3D11 currently hard-codes scaled accessors.
